title: Moments leading up to fatal shooting by officer
text:
Published By: USATODAY.com: Nation - Yesterday 
Video from inside Officer Vanessa Miller's vehicle shows the moments leading up to the fatal shooting of 28-year-old Ryan Keith Bolinger.
